### Parking Reservations
### ---------------------------------

### Parking Reservations - Get all
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations
Accept: application/json

###

### Parking Reservations - Get by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Parking Reservations - Create
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "visitId": 1,
  "slotId": 1,
  "vehiclePlate": "T123ABC"
}

###

### Parking Reservations - Update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "slotId": 1,
  "vehiclePlate": "T123ABC",
  "status": 2
}

###

### Parking Reservations - Release
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations/1/release
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "releasedAt": "2026-06-29T12:30:00Z"
}

###

### Parking Reservations - Cancel
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{}

###

### Parking Reservations - Delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/parkingreservations/1
Accept: application/json
